      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic restoration. The exterior shows significant signs of age, including noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, several large dents, and widespread clear coat failure. Inside, the cabin has seen heavy use; the upholstery is torn in multiple places, the headliner is sagging, and several interior trim pieces are missing or broken. Mechanically, the engine has a persistent knock and the transmission exhibits slipping, meaning it is not currently reliable for daily driving. This is strictly a project vehicle for someone with the tools and time to rebuild it.",
