    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really great shape, both inside and out. It\u2019s super fun to drive, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming road trips! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014I\u2019m sure it\u2019ll be the perfect fit for you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
