    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable companion, meticulously cared for and kept in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood consistent with typical highway driving. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and the premium surround-sound audio, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in great shape; it has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the brake pads were recently replaced. The tires have significant tread remaining, ensuring a smooth, quiet, and safe ride. I have maintained a comprehensive folder of all service records which will be passed on to the new owner. This is a solid, honest vehicle that perfectly balances high-end luxury with everyday practicality.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
