      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained specimen that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive multi-point technical evaluation to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. Offering a sophisticated synthesis of engineering excellence and sustained care, it represents an outstanding opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a premium automotive investment.",
      "price": 34800.0,
