    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. The interior is nice and clean, and it still drives like a dream! It's the perfect fit for anyone looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
