    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering power to the rear wheels via a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to an upgraded Bilstein B16 coilover setup and recent poly-bushing of the rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure. The engine pull is linear and strong up to the 8,000 RPM redline, with a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service documented. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, it strikes the perfect balance of a driver-focused machine that has been maintained with mechanical longevity in mind.",
